OL,7,FShe is on the front line of and crime.
OL,8,FShe shows me her phone camera-reel
OL,9,Fwhich is full of CCTV footage and
OL,10,Fstill images of incidents at her shop,
OL,11,Fwhere staff are regularly threatened
OL,12,Fand products are to sell on.
OL,14,FShe has an album of "Shoplifters"
OL,15,Fdedicated to the cause, so if a known
OL,16,Foffender comes in, she can ask them to
OL,17,Fleave the shop.
