OL,3,C'Zero-tolerance crime zones': Will
OL,4,CLabour's crackdown plans win over
OL,5,Cvoters?
OL,7,FThe vision is to have local high-
OL,8,Fstreet policing plans, where local
OL,9,Fbusinesses and residents can input
OL,10,Finto how areas are policed and new
OL,11,Fzero tolerance zones to clamp down on
OL,12,Fstreet drinking.
OL,14,FLabour say this will be paid for by
OL,15,Fefficiency savings in police
OL,16,Fprocurement of vehicles, IT and kit.
