OL,3,C'Zero-tolerance crime zones': Will
OL,4,CLabour's crackdown plans win over
OL,5,Cvoters?
OL,7,FThis seat has always been a Labour
OL,8,Fseat, until 2019, when it elected a
OL,9,FTory MP for the first time.
OL,11,FWe met residents Mickey and Denise,
OL,12,Fwho have formed a campaign group
OL,13,Fcalled Big Power for Little London, a
OL,14,Fnickname they have for their estate.
OL,16,FThey have held protest events and they
OL,17,Fare urging politicians to listen. They
OL,18,Fsay there is a link between the
OL,19,Fquality of the housing they have and
OL,20,Flevels of anti-social behaviour.
