OL,3,C'Zero-tolerance crime zones': Will
OL,4,CLabour's crackdown plans win over
OL,5,Cvoters?
OL,7,FWe chatted next to a building they
OL,8,Fcalled "The Derelicts", which is due
OL,9,Fto be redeveloped in the second half
OL,10,Fof 2024 - but the locals are not
OL,11,Fhopeful.
OL,13,FMickey and Denise told me that visited
OL,14,Fthe town in March, but they weren't
OL,15,Fallowed into the hotel where the prime
OL,16,Fminister held a question and answer
OL,17,Fsession with local people.
OL,19,FAlthough Maltby elected a Tory MP in
OL,20,Fthe 2019 election, it is a Labour
OL,21,Fheartland.
