OL,3,C'Zero-tolerance crime zones': Will
OL,4,CLabour's crackdown plans win over
OL,5,Cvoters?
OL,7,FWe spoke to many past Labour voters.
OL,8,FNot all of them had made their mind up
OL,9,Fabout where to place their vote on
OL,10,FJuly 4, but many told us that it is
OL,11,Ftime for a change.
OL,13,FEbony has never voted before. She told
OL,14,Fme she has seen a lot of material from
OL,15,FLabour on her social media channels,
OL,16,Fbut wants to find out more before
OL,17,Fpotentially casting her first ever
OL,18,Fvote.
